To install:

do 

	$ make;
	# will generate startup.pl and httpd.conf

and 

	$ cat httpd.conf >> /etc/http/httpd.conf;

(or whatever is the site to put your apache configuration in your distribution)

-- 
Perl modules you will need:

PerlIO		(by default).
Carp		(by default).
CGI		(by default).
File::Find	(by default)

Apache::Constants 
Apache::Request (depends on libapreq)
Text::Markdown 
